Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年会有chiroru的圣诞蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(chiroru 小鸠打工的蛋糕店)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让君在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它能装进更多礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事

